<lb n="0414b09" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0414b0901">唵<note place="inline">引</note><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0414002" n="0414002"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0414002" n="0414002"/><anchor xml:id="beg0414002" n="0414002"/>羅<anchor xml:id="end0414002"/>怛那<note place="inline">二合</note>三摩<note place="inline">引</note>提沒嚕<note place="inline">二合引</note>呬<note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0414b10" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0414b1001">唵<note place="inline">引</note>囉怛那<note place="inline">二合引</note>吠<note place="inline">引</note>舍捺哩舍<note place="inline"><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0414003" n="0414003"/><anchor xml:id="beg0414003" n="0414003"/>二合<anchor xml:id="end0414003"/></note>野<note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0414b11" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT18p0414b1101"><l>大印依法而相合</l><l>是印於身作纏繞</l>
<lb n="0414b12" ed="T"/><l>隨彼所有寶藏處</l><l>當知自三昧所現</l>
<lb n="0414b13" ed="T"/><l>若結最勝三昧印</l><l>當作警悟明開示</l>
<lb n="0414b14" ed="T"/><l>隨彼所有伏藏處</l><l>大寶莊嚴悉皆得</l>
<lb n="0414b15" ed="T"/><l>若結三摩地印契</l><l>隨警悟已智自說</l>
<lb n="0414b16" ed="T"/><l>由說某處有伏藏</l><l>大寶莊嚴悉皆得</l>
<lb n="0414b17" ed="T"/><l>若結羯磨大印契</l><l>由作警悟三昧法</l>
<lb n="0414b18" ed="T"/><l>二手互相作縛時</l><l>隨處伏藏當出現</l></lg>
<lb n="0414b19" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0414b1901">此等大明曰。</p>
